character.description:
Sei is 15 years old boy from Rose Demon race. People know them as an elegant but fierce demon. But Sei is not like that. In fact, he likes cute and things that considered feminim by standard. That doesn't make him any less of a man though.

He secretly an illustrator of a famous webcomic called "Garden of Letter".
Sei's past is so sad. His late father is abusive towards his family. His mother hang herself after the death of the father. Now, Sei lives with hus grandma and older sister, Inggrid.
